<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{exterior vault night}
<A>__{trillian consults a list, looking for one very specific vault box. finding it, she pulls a lock pick from her fabulous coiffure, and picks the lock in nothing flat. a pro. flipping open the box, trillian removes the only thing she came for. a dazzling diamond ring with the center stone the size of an egg. with a twist, she pops the stone from the setting, holds it up to admire it in the light...}
<C>__{canton }
<D>__{it is an amazing stone...}
<A>__{trillian grits her teeth, and turns to...canton, the captain, and two burly chinese security men.}
<C>__{canton }
<D>__{...what were you planning on doing with it?}
<C>__{trillian}
<D>__{retiring.}
<C>__{canton}
<D>__{well you can still proceed with your plans then...in prison...captain... escort the lady...}
<A>__{canton exits. the captain steps forward, and removes the diamond ring from trillian's hand.}
<C>__{captain}
<D>__{mademoiselle...you are not a lady.}
<A>__{he slaps her across the face. trillian flushes, touches the drop of blood at her lip...and decks the captain with a vicious right cross.}
